{"tid":2515706,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"台積電將應美方要求於亞利桑那州興建6座晶圓廠","createTime":"2021-05-04T07:17:43.000Z","updateTime":"2021-05-04T07:19:46.000Z","uid":28765,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"9991c1ac89a413c45fea35de4b5977a72e977ee5","tid":2515706,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T07:17:43.000Z","msg":"3名因未被授權與媒體交談而不願具名的消息人士向《路透》表示，台積電正在計劃為在亞利桑那州增加多達5座晶圓廠。當地首座晶圓廠相對於業界標準而言相對較小，計劃使用該公司最先進5奈米半導體製造技術，每月計劃生產2萬個晶圓，每個晶圓包含數千個晶片。<br />\n<br />\n....<br />\n<br />\n1位對此事有直接了解的知情人士表示，這一擴張決定是應美方要求做出的，但拒絕提供進一步的細節。該知情人士說：「美國要求這樣做。台積電內部計劃建造多達6個晶圓廠。」他補充說，台積電不可能給出時間表。<br />\n<br />\n全球最大晶圓代工廠台積電於2020年5月宣布，將在亞利桑那州建造1座價值120億美元的工廠，這顯然是川普政府在推動從中國手中奪回全球科技供應鏈的努力中獲得的勝利。<br />\n<br />\n....<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/property/20210504/PVGQLJRPSVAZFMHADWOJAABPO4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fproperty%2F20210504%2FPVGQLJRPSVAZFMHADWOJAABPO4%2F&d=4vQCcaBbFH%2F4J6PBkjxGnkv%2FgUeHX8FRhdV3zHjzpFI%3D&h=05026b1f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fproperty%2F20210504%2FPVGQLJRPSVAZFMHADWOJAABPO4%2F&h=02996c72\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/property/20210504/PVGQLJRPSVAZFMHADWOJAABPO4/</a>"},{"pid":"6a4c206cb17483338c344087e0fff418e535a0c3","tid":2515706,"uid":54681,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T07:19:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}